                                        <h1 class="h1 post-topheader__info--title" id="articleTitle" data-id="1190000008921805">
                                            <a href="/a/1190000008921805"> 《Web全栈工程师的自我修养》浓缩笔记（上）</a>
                                        </h1>

                                        <div class="content__tech hidden-xs">
